- YOU'RE NOT A DUMB FUCK, ARE YOU, DEL ?

216
00:14:30,286 --> 00:14:32,788
- NO.
- SO, GIVE ME AN EXAMPLE...

217
00:14:32,788 --> 00:14:35,791
OF A STUPID PERSON
