ANOTHER EXAMPLE. - THIS IS BULLSHIT.

232
00:15:19,451 --> 00:15:21,953
CAN WE GET DOWN
TO BUSINESS HERE, PLEASE ? JESUS CHRIST !

233
00:15:21,954 --> 00:15:25,457
- HE'S WAITING.
- OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

234
00:15:25,457 --> 00:15:27,459
- I DON'T KNOW.
