240
00:15:43,359 --> 00:15:45,861
KICKAPOO AND OSAGE.

241
00:15:45,861 --> 00:15:48,864
AM I RIGHT ABOUT THAT ?

242
00:15:49,865 --> 00:15:52,367
- I DON'T KNOW.
- YOU DON'T KNOW ?

243
00:15:52,368 --> 00:15:54,370
DEL,

244
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:56,872
MY IDEA OF STUPID'S
DIFFERENT FROM YOURS,

245
00:15:56,872 --> 00:15:59,374
SO HERE'S HOW
THIS IS GOING TO WORK.

246
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:01,493
TAKE YOUR SOCKS OFF.

247
00:16:01,493 --> 00:16:03,995
- [ Whimpering ]
- [ Sobbing ]

248
00:16:03,996 --> 00:16:06,498
HEY, COME ON.

249
00:16:06,498 --> 00:16:09,501
I'M SORRY.
IT'S MY FAULT.

250
00:16:09,501 --> 00:16:12,003
I THOUGHT YOU FELT
SOMETHING FOR ME.

251
00:16:12,004 --> 00:16:14,006
CHLOE,
YOU'RE WONDERFUL.

252
00:16:14,006 --> 00:16:16,508
YOU ARE.

253
00:16:16,508 --> 00:16:19,010
I JUST KNOW THAT THERE'S...

254
00:16:19,011 --> 00:16:21,513
SOMETHING REALLY SPECIAL
OUT THERE FOR ME.

255
00:16:21,513 --> 00:16:24,516
<i>I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT IS</i>
<i>OR WHO IT IS.</i>

256
00:16:24,516 --> 00:16:29,020
<i>I JUST KNOW THAT SINCE</i>
<i>LESLIE DIED, I'VE HAD</i> <i>THIS FEELING.</i>

257
00:16:29,021 --> 00:16:31,773
NOW, DEL, I'M GONNA TELL YOU
WHAT STUPID IS. [ Whimpering ]

258
00:16:32,157 --> 00:16:34,659
STUPID IS TAKING WHAT
DOESN'T BELONG TO YOU.

259
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:37,279
- ISN'T THAT RIGHT, WESLEY ?
- THAT'S RIGHT.

260
00:16:37,413 --> 00:16:39,415
