UNTRUSTWORTHY.

262
00:16:42,034 --> 00:16:46,038
- THAT IS SO RIGHT.
- STUPID, DEL, IS CALLING PEOPLE IN KANSAS CITY...

263
00:16:46,038 --> 00:16:50,042
