TAKE A KNIFE AND-- DEL.

275
00:17:27,329 --> 00:17:30,332
- COME ON, NOW.
WE'RE JUST TALKING HERE. - <i>[ Del Whimpering ]</i>

276
00:17:30,332 --> 00:17:33,335
COME ON.  JUST TAKE A KNIFE,
AND YOU MAKE...

277
00:17:33,335 --> 00:17:35,337
