OF THE FOREHEAD,

278
00:17:35,337 --> 00:17:38,840
GRAB A HANDFUL OF HAIR
AND CUT AS YOU PULL.

279
00:17:38,841 --> 00:17:41,343
IT'S AMAZING HOW EASILY
THE SCALP COMES OFF.

280
00:17:42,344 --> 00:17:44,346
A MARK, HUH ?

281
00:17:46,348 --> 00:17:49,601
IT'S OKAY, DAVID.
I MEAN, WHAT DO I KNOW ? SHH.

282
00:17:49,601 --> 00:17:53,104
A WOMAN GETS IN YOUR CAR,
YOU TAKE HER FOR A RIDE IN THE WOODS--

283
00:17:53,105 --> 00:17:56,608
- WAIT A MINUTE.
THIS WAS YOUR IDEA. - WHO'S DRIVING THE CAR, DAVID ?

284
00:17:56,608 --> 00:17:58,610
- WHAT ?
- DOES IT REALLY MATTER...

285
00:17:58,610 --> 00:18:01,112
- WHO SAID WHAT ?
- OF COURSE IT MATTERS.

286
00:18:01,113 --> 00:18:04,116
NOW I WANT TO KNOW
THE PARTICULARS OF YOUR WRONGDOING.

287
00:18:04,116 --> 00:18:06,618
I WANT TO KNOW HOW YOU GOT
WHAT YOU'VE STOLEN,

288
00:18:06,618 --> 00:18:10,121
- AND, OF COURSE,
WHERE IT IS NOW. - [ Muffled Speech ]

289
00:18:12,124 --> 00:18:16,628
<i>[ Gasping ]</i>
<i>IT'S IN THE BUICK.</i>

290
00:18:16,628 --> 00:18:20,632
BUT I SWEAR TO GOD,
I DIDN'T TOUCH IT. I SWEAR TO GOD !

291
00:18:20,632 --> 00:18:23,134
ALL RIGHT THEN.
<i>[ Sobbing ]</i> <i>DON'T KILL ME !</i>

292
00:18:23,135 --> 00:18:25,637
<i>I DON'T WANT YOU</i>
<i>TO KILL ME !</i>

293
00:18:25,637 --> 00:18:29,140
CONSIDER YOURSELF LUCKY, DEL.

294
00:18:29,141 --> 00:18:33,645
LUCKIER THAN THOSE INJUNS
YOU'VE GOT SUCH CONTEMPT FOR.

295
00:18:33,645 --> 00:18:37,532
