IT WAS THE AMERICAN INDIAN.

296
00:18:40,035 --> 00:18:43,538
THE COUNTRY HAS A BLACK MARK
ON ITS SOUL FOR WHAT HAPPENED TO THEM.

297
00:18:43,655 --> 00:18:46,908
<i>I'M GLAD THEY GOT</i>
<i>THOSE CASINOS.</i>

298
00:18:46,909 --> 00:18:49,912
<i>DAVID, I WISH I HAD</i>
<i>GOOD NEWS FOR YOU.</i>

299
00:18:50,412 --> 00:18:53,415
[ Del Groaning ]
