300
00:18:53,415 --> 00:18:57,419
CHLOE JENSEN HAS FILED CHARGES
OF SEXUAL ASSAULT AGAINST YOU.

301
00:19:01,056 --> 00:19:03,174
<i>[ Muffled Screaming ]</i>

302
00:19:08,931 --> 00:19:11,817
[ Both Screaming ]

303
00:19:11,934 --> 00:19:14,937
FUCKING CHRIST, WESLEY !

304
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:17,439
ARE YOU OUT
OF YOUR FUCKING MIND ?

305
00:19:20,442 --> 00:19:22,944
