WITH YOU ?

306
00:19:33,088 --> 00:19:35,340
WHAT THE FUCK
IS YOUR PROBLEM ?

307
00:19:35,841 --> 00:19:40,212
<i>YOU TOLD ME TO DO IT !</i>
<i>THAT WAS TO GET HIM</i> <i>TO TALK, YOU--</i>

308
00:19:40,345 --> 00:19:43,965
