THEN, I CAN FORGET.

310
00:19:50,472 --> 00:19:54,609
YOU EVER FEEL LIKE SOMETHING
REALLY SPECIAL WAS ABOUT TO HAPPEN TO YOU, JASMINE ?

311
00:19:55,611 --> 00:19:57,613
FUCKING GREAT, WESLEY !

312
00:19:58,113 --> 00:20:00,115
NOW WE DON'T KNOW WHERE
