- <i>[ Wesley ]  WELL, HE SAID</i>
<i>IT'S IN THE BUICK.</i> <i>- WHICH FUCKING BUICK ?</i>

314
00:20:02,734 --> 00:20:05,737
WHY'D YOU SHOOT HIM ?

315
00:20:05,737 --> 00:20:07,739
I HAD TO SHOOT HIM,
WESLEY.

316
00:20:07,739 --> 00:20:10,742
IT WAS THE ONLY
DECENT THING TO DO-- AFTER YOU SCALPED HIM !

317
00:20:12,878 --> 00:20:16,131
[ Echoing ]
I JUST KNOW THAT THERE'S SOMETHING REALLY SPECIAL--

318
00:20:16,131 --> 00:20:20,135
- ...REALLY SPECIAL
OUT THERE FOR ME. - VERY UNPROFESSIONAL, WESLEY !

319
00:20:20,636 --> 00:20:24,256
I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT IS
OR WHO IT IS.

320
00:20:24,506 --> 00:20:29,427
I JUST KNOW
THAT SINCE LESLIE DIED, I'VE HAD THIS FEELING.

321
00:20:33,432 --> 00:20:35,817
I JUST KNOW THAT THERE'S
SOMETHING REALLY SPECIAL...

322
00:20:35,817 --> 00:20:37,935
OUT THERE FOR ME.

323
00:20:37,936 --> 00:20:40,939
I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT IS.
I JUST KNOW THAT SINCE LESLIE DIED,

324
00:20:40,939 --> 00:20:45,443
I'VE HAD THIS FEELING.

325
00:20:55,454 --> 00:20:57,456
