326
00:20:59,458 --> 00:21:01,460
[ Singsong Voice ]
BETTY.

327
00:21:02,961 --> 00:21:04,963
[ Sue Ann Screams ]

328
00:21:05,213 --> 00:21:06,964
<i>[ Men Talking,</i>
<i>Police Radio Chatter ]</i>

329
00:21:14,723 --> 00:21:16,725
HEY, BETTY.
HI.

330
00:21:16,725 --> 00:21:19,728
- ARE YOU OKAY ?
- I'M GREAT.

331
00:21:19,728 --> 00:21:21,863
I WAS KIND OF WONDERING...

332
00:21:21,863 --> 00:21:25,366
IF I MIGHT BE ABLE
TO ASK SOME QUESTIONS ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED.

333
00:21:25,367 --> 00:21:28,370
WELL, I SAW THE WHOLE THING.
IT WAS DISGUSTING.

334
00:21:28,370 --> 00:21:31,489
- REALLY ?
DID YOU SEE WHO DID IT ? - MM-HMM.

335
00:21:31,490 --> 00:21:34,242
YOU DID ?  WHO WAS IT ?

336
00:21:34,242 --> 00:21:36,244
IT WAS CHLOE.

337
00:21:41,249 --> 00:21:44,502
YOU GUYS WANT TO TRY
<i>NOT</i> STEPPING DIRECTLY IN THE EVIDENCE, PLEASE ?

338
00:21:49,141 --> 00:21:51,143
ROY OSTREY !

339
00:21:51,143 --> 00:21:53,145
YOU AND YOUR GODDAMN
POLICE SCANNER.

340
00:21:53,145 --> 00:21:55,147
I LEAVE HERE
FOR TEN MINUTES--

341
00:21:55,147 --> 00:21:58,150
BETTY, I'M SORRY
ABOUT THIS.

342
00:21:58,150 --> 00:22:00,152
OH, IT'S NO PROBLEM.

343
00:22:00,152 --> 00:22:02,654
WELL, BYE, ROY.

344
00:22:02,654 --> 00:22:04,656
NICE TO SEE YOU, SHERIFF.

345
00:22:07,159 --> 00:22:09,661
THANKS FOR STOPPING BY.

346
00:22:14,166 --> 00:22:16,535
WHERE THE HELL
IS SHE GOING ?

347
00:22:16,535 --> 00:22:20,539
[ Wesley ]
I STILL DON'T UNDERSTAND HOW YOU KNEW DEL WASN'T LYING.

348
00:22:20,539 --> 00:22:22,541
I SAW HIS SOUL, WESLEY.

349
00:22:22,541 --> 00:22:24,543
THE MAN WAS FACE TO FACE
WITH HIS GOD.

350
00:22:24,543 --> 00:22:27,045
NOBODY LIES
IN THAT SITUATION.

351
00:22:27,045 --> 00:22:29,047
YOUR LITTLE GERONIMO ACT
RATTLED ME,

352
00:22:29,047 --> 00:22:31,049
AND I ABANDONED
MY INSTINCTS.

353
00:22:31,049 --> 00:22:33,051
NEVER ABANDON
YOUR INSTINCTS. I DIDN'T.

354
00:22:33,552 --> 00:22:36,054
YOU GAVE ME A LOOK.
WHAT FUCKIN' LOOK ?

355
00:22:36,304 --> 00:22:38,306
<i>YOU ONLY GOT ONE LOOK.</i>
<i>YOU GAVE ME THIS LOOK.</i>

356
00:22:38,306 --> 00:22:40,308
I THOUGHT YOU WERE DONE
SO I OFFED HIM.

357
00:22:40,308 --> 00:22:42,810
WELL, I WASN'T DONE.
I WAS JUST TIRED OF HEARING HIM WHINE.

358
00:22:43,311 --> 00:22:46,314
AND YOU DIDN'T
OFF ANYBODY, BUDDY. YOU SCALPED HIM.

359
00:22:46,314 --> 00:22:48,816
JESUS, I ALMOST PUKED.
DID I TELL YOU THAT ?

360
00:22:48,817 --> 00:22:50,819
