THE FUCKING INDIAN STORY ?

361
00:22:50,819 --> 00:22:53,321
WHAT THE HELL
DOES THAT MEAN, WESLEY ?

362
00:22:53,321 --> 00:22:55,823
IF I TOLD YOU A TY COBB STORY,
WOULD YOU HAVE TAKEN A BASEBALL BAT...

363
00:22:55,824 --> 00:22:58,326
AND BEATEN HIM TO DEATH ?
YOU--

364
00:22:58,326 --> 00:23:00,328
GODDAMN !

365
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:03,832
<i>NOTHIN' THERE.</i>
<i>LET'S GO.</i>

366
00:23:03,832 --> 00:23:06,835
- YOU GONNA JUST LEAVE
THE CARS LIKE THIS ? - YEAH, WHY NOT ?

367
00:23:06,835 --> 00:23:08,837
IT'LL CONFUSE 'EM.

368
00:23:08,837 --> 00:23:10,839
GOTTA DO SOMETHING,
NOW THAT YOU'VE FUCKED IT UP.

369
00:23:10,839 --> 00:23:13,341
I DIDN'T FUCK NOTHIN' UP.
I WAS JUST TRYING TO MAKE A STATEMENT.

370
00:23:13,341 --> 00:23:15,843
TRYING TO MAKE
A STATEMENT.

371
00:23:16,344 --> 00:23:18,346
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHING.

372
00:23:18,346 --> 00:23:20,848
IN THIS BUSINESS,
YOU DON'T PUT FOOD ON THE TABLE...

373
00:23:20,849 --> 00:23:22,851
UNLESS THE PHONE RINGS.

374
00:23:22,851 --> 00:23:26,855
THE PEOPLE WHO
GET THE CALLS ARE GOOD-- NOT FLASHY, GOOD.

375
00:23:26,855 --> 00:23:28,857
THEY GET IN, THEY GET OUT,
NOBODY KNOWS A GODDAMN THING.

376
00:23:28,857 --> 00:23:31,359
YOU UNDERSTAND ?
BOOM, BOOM, BOOM.

377
00:23:31,359 --> 00:23:33,861
THREE IN THE HEAD,
YOU KNOW THEY'RE DEAD.

378
00:23:35,363 --> 00:23:38,366
THAT'S A GOOD MOTTO.
WELL, I'LL GET YOU A BUMPER STICKER.

379
00:23:38,867 --> 00:23:42,871
YOU BETTER START BELIEVING IT.
THAT'S THE ONLY STATEMENT YOU NEED TO MAKE.

380
00:23:46,374 --> 00:23:48,709
<i>IS THIS BOTHERING YOU ?</i>

381
00:23:49,094 --> 00:23:51,096
LET'S GET
THIS THING DOWN. THANK YOU.

382
00:23:51,596 --> 00:23:53,598
PSST.

383
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:58,603
I QUESTIONED JOYCE
ABOUT ALL THIS. YEAH ?

384
00:23:58,603 --> 00:24:01,105
IT SEEMS SHE WAS
PRETTY FAMILIAR WITH OLD DEL--

385
00:24:01,106 --> 00:24:03,608
ON A REGULAR BASIS,
IF YOU GET MY DRIFT.

386
00:24:03,608 --> 00:24:06,110
AND HALF THE OTHER GUYS
IN THIS TOWN, INCLUDING YOURSELF, I BELIEVE.

387
00:24:06,111 --> 00:24:08,613
JUNIOR YEAR.
ANYWAY, SO WHAT ?

388
00:24:08,613 --> 00:24:12,116
SO, SUPPOSE BETTY
FOUND OUT ABOUT THEM.

389
00:24:13,618 --> 00:24:17,121
SO YOU'RE SAYING
THAT BETTY SIZEMORE--

390
00:24:17,122 --> 00:24:21,126
OUR BETTY SIZEMORE,
WHO YOU WENT TO SWING CHOIR WITH--

391
