IN AMERICAN ? - IT'S A KIND OF ALTERED STATE.

399
00:24:49,654 --> 00:24:52,657
IT ALLOWS
A TRAUMATIZED PERSON TO CONTINUE FUNCTIONING.

400
00:24:53,158 --> 00:24:56,161
- SO SHE DID WITNESS IT ?
- <i>[ Doctor ]</i> <i>WITHOUT QUESTION.</i>

401
00:24:56,161 --> 00:24:58,663
<i>BUT HER MEMORY OF IT</i>
<i>HAS GONE.</i>

402
00:24:58,663 --> 00:25:01,666
<i>ANY IDEA WHO CHLOE</i>
<i>OR LONNIE ARE ?</i>

403
00:25:07,172 --> 00:25:09,174
