EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE FINE.

408
00:25:27,058 --> 00:25:30,061
OH, I KNOW.

409
00:25:30,061 --> 00:25:33,564
AND I'M REAL SORRY
ABOUT ALL THIS.

410
00:25:35,567 --> 00:25:40,572
BUT I JUST KNOW THERE'S
SOMETHING SPECIAL OUT THERE FOR ME.

411
00:26:02,928 --> 00:26:04,930
[ Betty's Voice ]
DEAR DEL.

412
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:08,183
[ Thinking ]
