459
00:29:03,108 --> 00:29:05,860
NO, NOT QUITE.

460
00:29:05,860 --> 00:29:09,363
ANYWAY, SHE'S BEEN WITH US
QUITE A WHILE.

461
00:29:09,864 --> 00:29:12,366
