THE ACTOR ?

546
00:34:26,347 --> 00:34:29,850
NO.  NO, NO, NO.
DAVID RAVELL.

547
00:34:29,851 --> 00:34:31,853
HE'S A HEART SPECIALIST.

548
00:34:31,853 --> 00:34:33,855
I KNOW.
WE JUST WATCHED HIM.

549
00:34:42,864 --> 00:34:44,866
YOU'RE SERIOUS.

550
00:34:47,869 --> 00:34:49,871
HOW ARE YOU GONNA
FIND HIM, BETTY ?

551
00:34:49,871 --> 00:34:52,874
WELL, I'LL--
