578
00:36:51,792 --> 00:36:53,794
<i>PERFECT FORM.</i>

579
00:36:53,794 --> 00:36:55,796
YEAH.

580
00:36:55,796 --> 00:36:58,799
SUCH POISE TOO.

581
00:36:58,799 --> 00:37:00,801
