589
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:32,083
<i>WELL, MR. AND MRS. BLAINE,</i>
<i>I CAN ASSURE YOU,</i> <i>WITHOUT A DOUBT,</i>

590
00:37:32,583 --> 00:37:34,585
